text: haey avei del a l laoh ban bratan chea chyophond aoy anak noam sar robsa trong ampi( tropy sa mb tde) puokke noh ku puok anak minban chamnay seh muoy kbal ryy satv audth muoy kbal samreab chiah yk tow chbang laey . bo nde a l laoh phdal anoupheap dl banda anakneasar robsa trong towleu anaknea del trong mean chetnea . haey a l laoh mean anoupheap leu avei teangoasa
